during his graduation speech.

694
00:51:36,259 --> 00:51:38,261
When someone feels nervous or excited,

695
00:51:38,328 --> 00:51:39,796
his blood pressure goes up.

696
00:51:40,297 --> 00:51:41,631
The second time was

697
00:51:42,165 --> 00:51:44,501
when he stayed up
for three nights working.

698
00:51:44,634 --> 00:51:46,069
The last one was...

